<div id="title">
  Part of Speech Tagging
</div>

<div id="body">
  <div class="modal-body">
      <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        A <span class="font-semibold">Part of Speech tag</span> identifies the grammatical role of a word within a sentence —
        such as whether it is a <span class="font-medium">noun</span>, <span class="font-medium">verb</span>,
        <span class="font-medium">adjective</span>, or <span class="font-medium">preposition</span>.
        In Quranic linguistic analysis, POS tagging helps classify each word according to its syntactic function,
        enabling deeper grammatical study, automated parsing, and linguistic comparison across translations.
      </p>

    <div class="bg-yellow-50 border-yellow-400 rounded-r-xl p-4 max-w-2xl mt-4">
